 3ï¸âƒ£ What is Nitro System

Definition:
AWS Nitro System ek modern virtualization platform hai jo EC2 ko fast, secure aur scalable banata hai.

Nitro kya karta hai:

â†’ Hypervisor ko lightweight banata hai
â†’ Hardware offloading karta hai (network, storage, security)
â†’ Performance better hoti hai
â†’ Customer ka data AWS se isolate rehta hai
â†’ Bare-metal jaisi speed milti hai

Simple language:
Nitro = EC2 ke liye high-performance engine

