 4ï¸âƒ£ Amazon EBS Volume

EBS Volume = Virtual Hard Disk

â†’ EC2 instance ke saath attach hoti hai
â†’ Ek time me ek instance se attach hoti hai (mostly)
â†’ AZ specific hoti hai
â†’ Snapshot ke through backup le sakte ho

---

 5ï¸âƒ£ EBS Volume Types

 ğŸŸ¢ SSD Based Volumes (High Performance)

Use case: OS, Database, Applications

â†’ gp2 / gp3 â€“ General Purpose
Balanced cost + performance
â†’ io1 / io2 â€“ Provisioned IOPS
High performance databases ke liye
â†’ io2 Block Express
Mission-critical workloads

---

 ğŸ”µ HDD Based Volumes (Throughput Optimized)

Use case: Large data, backup, logs

â†’ st1 â€“ Throughput Optimized HDD
â†’ sc1 â€“ Cold HDD (low cost, archival type data)

