 6ï¸âƒ£ EBS Volume vs Instance Store

| Feature         | Instance Store | EBS                  |
| --------------- | -------------- | -------------------- |
| Persistence     | âŒ Temporary    | âœ… Permanent          |
| Backup          | âŒ No Snapshot  | âœ… Snapshot available |
| Use case        | Cache, temp    | OS, DB, App          |
| Data after stop | âŒ Lost         | âœ… Safe               |

